  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dae\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0db0\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dba \u0d8b\u0db4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db8 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1 30\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0db4\u0db8\u0dab\u0dba\u0dd2 - \u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2 \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd2 \u0d91\u0d9a\u0d9f \u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db0\u0dcf\u0db1 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Speaker's presidency for a maximum of 30 days only - 4 main points agreed in the party leaders' meeting",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been decided in the party leader meeting that the presidency will be offered to Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena for a maximum period of 30 days only. The party leaders have agreed on four basic points in this party leaders meeting.",
        "01 President Gotabhaya Rapaksha and Prime Minister Ranil Wickramasinghe immediately resign from their posts.",
        "03 Election of a Member of Parliament as President by the Parliament for the rest of the term",
        "Explaining this on his Twitter account, the Member of Parliament Mr. Harsha de Silva said that an interim government will be established soon."
      ],
